title: Generate Random Wishart Distribution — rwishart
code: #Call with the following data: rwishart(3, diag(2)) #>           [,1]      [,2] #> [1,]  2.350831 -2.351707 #> [2,] -2.351707  6.860861  # Validation set.seed(1337) S = toeplitz((10:1)/10) n = 10000 o = array(dim = c(10,10,n)) for(i in 1:n){ o[,,i] = rwishart(20, S) } mR = apply(o, 1:2, mean) Va = 20*(S^2 + tcrossprod(diag(S))) vR = apply(o, 1:2, var) stopifnot(all.equal(vR, Va, tolerance = 1/16))
